section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
Wifi 
PARIS
Sundance
Must be respectful to owner. 
You may use kitchen but if you don’t clean up after yourself kitchen privileges will be revoked. If you are working from my home you must use your room as your office. Common areas are not for your work area.
No cooking or heating of water in bedrooms. 
No pets.
No house guest. 
The only guests welcome are the ones stated on the time of booking.
This is not a party house.
No illegal drugs. Wine and beer ok. 
No longer than 15 minute showers. Otherwise charge $10 extra per day. 
No more than 2 suitcases
Do not take anything that is mine outside house. 
Do not leave anything of value in your car. You are responsible for anything missing. If your car leaks oil park car on street. If you bring more than lap top you will be charged an addition electrical charge. WiFi for personal use only using a laptop or iPhone. Not responsible for business high WiFi needs.
Check out time 11:00 am.
Fire extinguisher located under or by kitchen table.

section.about: I have lived in Los Angeles for years. I worked in the entertainment business for years. I love movies. I am a docent at the Getty Center Museum and Los Angelos Zoo and botanical gardens. I am very familiar with what to do here, theatre, tourist activities, beach, movies, restaurants and hiking. I have traveled all around the world and love talking about traveling. My house is very relaxing, clean and quiet. No drugs or smoking. Wine and beer ok.

hostHighlights.title: My work: Getty Center Museum and  Los Angelos Zoo and Botanical garden as a docent
I'm obsessed with: Flowers, painting, travel and animals.
What makes my home unique: Hundreds of flowers in Spring.

htmlDescription.htmlText:
Queen size bed, desk, dresser and mirrored closet.
Shared full size bathroom.
Shared kitchen and outside patio. There is a lock on door. Key entree.
Beautiful serene outside gardens.
High speed internet 300 Mbps.
Shared Wash machine and dryer for your use. This house is not available for student films.
Sorry, no pets. Short term Los Angeles #HSR22-000248 permit.

The space
Private and cozy room in Sherman Oaks area. Comfy queen size bed, desk, dresser, flat screen TV and closet space. Window looking out to the backyard garden.
300 Mbps for wifi
Full bathroom: Tub and Shower. (Shared with one other person)
Shared Kitchen. Refrigerator, microwave, big counter top, toaster, electric kettle and coffee maker.
You get one shelf in refrigerator and one shelf for dry storage.
Central air conditioning and heater.
Cottage garden style house. There are flowers and fruit trees all around the yard and the neighborhood. The garden is very relaxing. Patio tables and chairs to enjoy the garden.

This is listed as in Van Nuys but is actually in Sherman Oaks, Nice quiet neighborhood. Grocery stores, pharmacy, mall, restaurants and movie theaters are all very close. I listed a few, see below.

Restaurants in Sherman Oaks:

Carnival, Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, 4356 Woodman Ave

Tony's Mexican Grill, Mexican, 12910 Magnolia Blvd

Crave Cafe, Coffee, Desserts/Ice Cream, Sandwiches/Subs
14504 Ventura Blvd.

There is public transportation available 4 blocks away. The Orange line links up to the subway.

WiFi is only for basic personal internet for laptop and phone. Not for professional use. Downloading video or lots of material please find a business office for this or another place.

I do not allow any pets. Sorry.

Food Markets in Sherman Oaks:
Trader Joe's/14119 Riverside Dr (2.44 miles)
Ralph's /14440 Burbank Blvd, (1.1 mile)

Shopping:

Movie Theaters in Sherman Oaks:
Sherman Oaks Galleria, AcrLight/14 theaters, Ventura Blvd. (2 miles)
(Also has a Cheesecake factory and P.F. Chang's)

Pacific theaters Sherman Oaks (phone number hidden) Milbank St. (2.4 miles

Guest access
Kitchen, dining room and back yard patio.

During your stay
If you have any questions I am happy to help you. Otherwise, I will respect your privacy.

Other things to note
There may be another house guest in the house besides myself. They have their own bathroom.

License number
HSR22-000248

section.subtitle: AirCover is comprehensive protection included for free with every booking.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.

section.learnMoreTitle: Find complete details on how AirCover protects your booking in our %{link_start}Help Center%{link_end}
